Why Java for Selenium 
================================
-> Java is object oriented programing langauge(we can develop reusable component)
-> Java is plateform independent(works on all operating system)
-> Java is open source (partially)

Practical usage of arrays in Selenium 
===============================================
Array
ArrayList
List
	Data can be read and stored in above types of class and we can process/pass 

selenium webdriver (finder)


String names[] = {"nitin@gmail.com","divya@gmail.com","raman@gmail.com"};


WebDriver driver = new ChromeDriver();
for(String u : names){

	driver.get("https://www.gmail.com");
	driver.findElement(By.id("email")).sendKeys(u);
}



