FRAMEWORK : is standard approach to develop or implement the project
=======================================================================
-> Framework provideres pre-defined template/structure and library(APIs)

Junit : is framework which we can use for unit testing 

There are two types of classes:
	-Junit Test Class/Case
	-Junit TestSuite 		: collections of JunitTest Classes 
	

There are following annotation in Junit:
	@BeforeClass		: 1		-execute one time
	@AfterClass			: 5	-execute one time
	@Before			: 2		-before every @Test
	@After				: 4	-after every @Test	
	@Test 			: 3		-can be multiple 
	




